text: Gateway is a 1993 metal sculpture by Hans Van de Bovenkamp, installed in Oklahoma City's Myriad Botanical Gardens, in the U.S. state of Oklahoma. The abstract artwork was dedicated on November 16, 1993, and measures approximately 16 x 15 x 5 ft. ==See also== * 1993 in art ==References== Category:1993 establishments in Oklahoma Category:1993 sculptures Category:Abstract sculptures in the United States Category:Metal sculptures Category:Outdoor sculptures in Oklahoma City
title: Gateway (Van de Bovenkamp)
